<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<!-- Basic Page Needs
		–––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––– -->
		<meta charset="utf-8">
		<title>Dillon Brown / Portfolio</title>
		<meta name="description" content="">
		<meta name="author" content="">

		<!-- Mobile Specific Metas
		–––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––– -->
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">

		<!-- CSS
		–––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––– -->
		<link rel="stylesheet" href="css/main.css">
		<link rel="stylesheet" href="css/98.css">
		<style>
			.icon {
				text-align: center;
				color: white;
				cursor: pointer;
				margin: 12px;
				border: 1px dotted transparent;
			}
			.icon.active {
				border: 1px dotted black;
			}
			.icon p {
				margin: 0;
			}
			p {
				font-size: 1.25rem;
			}
			.window-body img {
				background: white;
				padding: 10px;
				box-shadow:
					inset -1px -1px #fff,
					inset 1px 1px #0a0a0a,
					inset -2px -2px grey,
					inset 2px 2px #dfdfdf;
			}
			.window {
				margin-bottom: 4rem;
			}
			a {
				color: #00f !important;
				text-decoration-color: #00f !important;
			}
		</style>

		<!-- Favicon
		–––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––– -->
		<link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="images/favicon.png">
		
		<!-- JavaScript
		–––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––– -->
	    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-1.12.4.js"></script>
		<script src="https://code.jquery.com/ui/1.12.1/jquery-ui.js"></script>
	    <script>
			$( function() {
				// Make windows draggable
				$(".draggable").draggable({
					handle: ".title-bar",
					stack: "main .draggable"
				});
			
				// Make close buttons work
				$("#closeWindow-intro").click(function() {
					$("#window-intro").hide();
				});
				$("#closeWindow-details").click(function() {
					$("#window-details").hide();
				});
				$("#closeWindow6").click(function() {
					$("#window6").hide();
				});
				$("#closeWindow5").click(function() {
					$("#window5").hide();
				});
				$("#closeWindow4").click(function() {
					$("#window4").hide();
				});
			
				// Icons
				$("#button6").click(function() {
					$("#button4, #button5, #button6").removeClass("active");
					$(this).addClass("active");
					
					$([document.documentElement, document.body]).animate({
						scrollTop: $("#window6").offset().top
					}, 2000);
				});
				$("#button5").click(function() {
					$("#button4, #button5, #button6").removeClass("active");
					$(this).addClass("active");
					
					$([document.documentElement, document.body]).animate({
						scrollTop: $("#window5").offset().top
					}, 2000);
				});
				$("#button4").click(function() {
					$("#button4, #button5, #button6").removeClass("active");
					$(this).addClass("active");
					
					$([document.documentElement, document.body]).animate({
						scrollTop: $("#window4").offset().top
					}, 2000);
				});
			} );
		</script>
</head>
<body>
	<header class="window">
		<nav style="display:block">
			<div style="display: flex;justify-content: space-evenly;end;">
				<div style="display: inline-flex;flex-grow: 2;">
					<button>
						<a href="/" class="bold-900">Dillon J. Brown</a>
					</button>
				</div>
				<div style="display: inline-flex;flex-grow: 0;">
					<button>
						<a href="mailto:hello@dillonbrown.me">Contact</a>
					</button>
				</div>
				<div style="display: inline-flex;flex-grow: 0;">
					<button>
						<a href="/pdf/resume.pdf">Résumé</a>
					</button>
				</div>
			</div>
		</nav>
	</header>
	<main>
		<div class="row">
			<!--
				Icons
			-->
			<div class="two columns">
				<div class="icon" id="button6">
					<img src="images/the-drugulator/icon_2.png">
					<p>Version 6.0</p>
				</div>
				
				<div class="icon" id="button5">
					<img src="images/the-drugulator/icon_1.png">
					<p>Version 5.0</p>
				</div>
				
				<div class="icon" id="button4">
					<img src="images/the-drugulator/icon_3.png">
					<p>Version 4.0</p>
				</div>
			</div>
			
			<!--
				Intro
			-->
			<div class="five offset-by-one columns">
				<div class="window draggable" id="window-intro">
					<div class="title-bar">
						<div class="title-bar-text">The Drugulator</div>
						<div class="title-bar-controls">
							<button aria-label="Close" id="closeWindow-intro"></button>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="window-body">
							<p>I found <a href="http://wiki.tripsit.me/wiki/Drug_combinations">this great chart</a> showing how (relatively) safe combinations of drugs can be. I knew I could use my web development know-how to improve it, so I made it into a web app.</p>
							<p>My web app is a pet project of mine and is constantly evolving. I do a rudimentary form of user testing on my friends whenever I make improvements. I also put the source code on GitHub for anyone to use in any way they want. This is for harm reduction and education, not profit.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
			
			<!--
				Details
			-->
			<div class="four columns">
				<div class="window draggable" id="window-details">
					<div class="title-bar">
						<div class="title-bar-text">Details</div>
						<div class="title-bar-controls">
							<button aria-label="Close" id="closeWindow-details"></button>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="window-body">
						<p><strong>Design & Development</strong><br>2016 &mdash; present<br></p>

						<button>
							<a href="https://dillonjohnbrown.github.io/drug-combos">Website</a>
						</button>
						<button>
							<a href="https://github.com/dillonjohnbrown/drug-combos">GitHub</a>
						</button>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
		
		<div class="row">
			<div class="twelve columns">
				<!--
					6.0
				-->
				<div class="window draggable" id="window6">
					<div class="title-bar">
						<div class="title-bar-text">Modern refinement</div>
						<div class="title-bar-controls">
							<button aria-label="Close" id="closeWindow6"></button>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="window-body">
						<div class="row">
							<div class="three columns">
								<h1>6.0</h1>
								<p>This revision was built mobile-first, with a focus on simplicity.</p>
							</div>
							<div class="nine columns">
								<a href="https://dillonjohnbrown.github.io/drug-combos">
									<img class="u-max-full-width" src="images/the-drugulator/6.png">
								</a>
							</div>
						</div>
						<div class="row">
							<div class="three columns">
								<p>I am extremely proud of this incarnation. I learned from the misteps of past versions and created a balanced, refined, and beautiful tool.</p>
								<p>I encourage you to <a href="https://dillonjohnbrown.github.io/drug-combos">take it for a test drive</a>.</p>
							</div>
							<div class="nine columns">
								<a href="https://dillonjohnbrown.github.io/drug-combos">
									<img class="u-max-full-width" src="images/the-drugulator/6-combo.png">
								</a>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
				
				<!--
					5.0
				-->
				<div class="window draggable" id="window5">
					<div class="title-bar">
						<div class="title-bar-text">Better, faster, smarter</div>
						<div class="title-bar-controls">
							<button aria-label="Close" id="closeWindow5"></button>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="window-body">
						<div class="row">
							<div class="three columns">
								<h1>5.0</h1>
								<p>In this revision I rebuilt the site from the ground up.</p>
								<p>The largest change was under the hood. I replaced <a href="https://github.com/dillonjohnbrown/drug-combos/blob/46af5e746aa139445e8d79969b07f9b638790612/js/main.js#L1">a fragile, hand-coded 2D JavaScript array</a>, with a <a href="https://github.com/TripSit/comboapp/blob/master/app/src/data/combo_beta.json">JSON file maintained by TripSit</a>.</p>
							</div>
							<div class="nine columns">
								<img class="u-max-full-width" src="images/the-drugulator/5.png">
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
				
				<!--
					4.0
				-->
				<div class="window draggable" id="window4">
					<div class="title-bar">
						<div class="title-bar-text">For designers, by designers, for no one</div>
						<div class="title-bar-controls">
							<button aria-label="Close" id="closeWindow4"></button>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="window-body">
						<div class="row">
							<div class="three columns">
								<h1>4.0</h1>
								<p>Users were unsure how to interact with this version, sentencing this design to the cutting room floor.</p>
								<p>When building this design I wanted to challenge myself by using only black and white. Left to my own devices, I went a little too far and usability suffered.</p>
							</div>
							<div class="nine columns">
								<img class="u-max-full-width" src="images/the-drugulator/4.png">
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</main>
</body>
</html>